quran[9{c,v,t}:
11,109,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, to un mabodon ki taraf se kisi shak mein nah reh jin ki yeh log ibadat kar rahay hain yeh to ( bas lakeer ke faqeer banay hue ) usi terhan pooja paat kiye ja rahay hain jis terhan pehlay un ke baap dada karte thay, aur hum inn ka hissa aِnhin bharpoor den ge baghair is ke ke is mein kuch kaat kasar ho"
11,110,hum is se pehlay moose ko bhi kitaab day chuke hain aur is ke baray mein bhi ikhtilaaf kya gaya tha ( jis terhan aaj iss kitaab ke baray mein kya ja raha hai jo tumhe di gayi hai ) agar tairay rab ki taraf se aik baat pehlay hi tey nah kar di gayi hoti to inn ikhtilaaf karne walon ke darmain kabhi ka faisla chuka diya gaya hota yeh waqea hai ke yeh log is ki taraf se shak aur Khuljan mein parre hue hain
11,111,"aur yeh bhi waqea hai ke tera rab inhen un ke aamaal ka poora poora badla day kar rahay ga, yaqeenan woh un ki sab harkato se bakhabar hai"
11,112,"pas ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum, aur tumahray woh saathi jo ( kufar o baghaawat se imaan o taat ki taraf ) palat aeye hain, theek theek raah raast par saabit qadam raho jaissa ke tumhe hukum diya gaya hai aur bandagi ki hadd se tajawaz nah karo jo kuch tum kar rahay ho is par tumhara rab nigah rakhta hai"
11,113,inn zaalmon ki taraf zara nah jhukna warna jahannum ki lapait mein aa jao ge aur tumhe koi aisa walii o sarparast nah miley ga jo khuda se tumhe bacha sakay aur kahin se tum ko madad nah puhanche gi
11,114,"aur dekho, namaz qaim karo din ke dono suron par aur kuch raat guzarnay par dar haqeeqat naikian buraiyon ko daur kar deti hain, yeh aik yaad dehani hai un logon ke liye jo khuda ko yaad rakhnay walay hain"
11,115,"aur sabr kar, Allah neki karne walon ka ajar kabhi zaya nahi karta"
11,116,"phir kyun nah unn qomon mein jo tum se pehlay guzar chuki hain aisay ahal kher mojood rahay jo logon ko zameen mein fasaad barpaa karne se roktay? aisay log niklay bhi to bohat kam, jin ko hum ne un qomon mein se bacha liya, warna zalim log to unhi mazonke peechay parre rahay jin ke samaan inhen farawani ke sath diye gay thay aur woh mujrim ban kar rahay"
11,117,tera rab aisa nahi hai ke bustiyon ko na-haq tabah kar day halaank un ke bashinday islaah karne walay hon
